This paper is about planning and implementing autonomous motion for rescue robots, which is a common topic in the field of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of parameter configuration of the scene, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV). The implementation of the algorithm on a real robot involves control systems (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques.
